{
  "stem": "11916.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was my nerve-- loneliness, sadness, the food and the cold-- where you sleep at night, which was cold, and daytime, the sun was killing you.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was really hot at daytime.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I don't really know what more.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Whenever you have any illness, you just kept quiet, because if you tell them or if they know it themselves, you look sick, that's the end of your life.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I wanted to live through, to hoping just to live through.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because my father also told us, when he saw me the last, it couldn't last too long, maybe another four weeks.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you might be able to hold on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was wrong.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was lasted another year.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Reichenbach is a smaller city, I think, was somewhere near Poland, or was maybe in Poland, more like Poland than Germany.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a city where all the prisoners working, many, many thousands of them in different camps they was living.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The most famous was the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was about three, four kilometers from the place I used to work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But where I live, it was almost about a 3/4 hour's walk only from the factory.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A radio factory.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was making lamps for radios or for boats.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was different kind of factories, many of them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I only knew the one I was working, because you're coming, talking with the other prisoners.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some was working fieldwork.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and in different factories, but they was all manufacturing for the war something, except the field workers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where I was living it was the best condition, I was told, whatever they gave to the prisoners, because this was a special lager where they even brought in the Red Cross sometimes, to show how the prisoners lived.",
      "word_count": 39
    }
  ],
